		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />here is a <a href="http://members.cox.net/theplaceicometobleed/backup/Pitfall.zip" class="postlink">beta</a> of the game (ntsc). there is no sound.
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />i don't have a chip programmer so if someone could test it on actual hardware i would greatly appreciate it (mmc1).
<br />
<br />controls for level editor:
<br />
<br />up, down: move cursor around current menu
<br />left, right: move cursor from menu to menu
<br />sel, start: cycle through scenes
<br />A: enter
<br />
<br />feedback would also be appreciated.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
