		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The only reason I offer critique is that this is a very promising-looking remake, worthy of polishing to perfection.
<br />
<br />Movement seems jerky (20 FPS?). I'd expect that the original ran at 60 FPS, but I may be wrong. Also, my emulator reported a possible sprite DMA while the PPU was active, but maybe it's not the case. Does it work on hardware?
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">The game handles a lot better than the original (Maybe since I'm not using a really annoying joystick).</div>
<br />If this is true, doesn't that mean the challenge of the original is lost?

		

